===真人電視劇===
{{main|惡靈古堡 (電視劇)}}
2019年1月，[[Netflix|Netflix]]宣佈基於生化危機系列開發衍生電視劇<ref name="Development">{{Cite web|last=Nellie|first=Andreeva|date=2019-01-24|title=‘Resident Evil’ TV Series In Works At Netflix|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/resident-evil-tv-series-in-works-netflix-1202541277/|access-date=2020-08-27|website=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191122011702/https://deadline.com/2019/01/resident-evil-tv-series-in-works-netflix-1202541277/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年8月，Netflix整季預訂該電視劇，共8集<ref name="PickedUp" />。{{le|安德魯·達布|Andrew Dabb}}擔當[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]，{{le|布朗溫·休斯|Bronwen Hughes}}執導前兩集<ref name="PickedUp">{{Cite web|last=Goldberg|first=Lesley|title='Resident Evil' TV Series Officially a Go at Netflix {{!}} Hollywood Reporter|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/resident-evil-tv-series-officially-a-go-at-netflix|date=2020-08-27|access-date=2020-08-27|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827183046/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/resident-evil-tv-series-officially-a-go-at-netflix|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

